{"tid":1645053,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實警察有無權係查身份証時要市民提供地址同電話?","createTime":"2019-10-10T18:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T19:01:08.000Z","uid":84394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"931ee83a53d674411b1f1735c318af34627ec024","tid":1645053,"uid":84394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:13:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jason.lam.1238/videos/2435211396534114/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjason.lam.1238%2Fvideos%2F2435211396534114%2F&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqdAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=373bbcf9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/jason.lam.1238/videos/2435211396534114/</a><br />\n事源睇左上面條片,個警察要求佢比電話同地址係因為公安條例,但又講唔到邊條,我就上網搵發現左只要未被捕,佢係無權拎地址喎,雖然個後生仔最後都係屈服左。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請大家班手求證我有無錯..?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n警察查閱身分證的權力| 楊岳橋| 立場新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%9F%A5%E9%96%B1%E8%BA%AB%E5%88%86%E8%AD%89%E7%9A%84%E6%AC%8A%E5%8A%9B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E6%259F%25A5%25E9%2596%25B1%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E5%2588%2586%25E8%25AD%2589%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%258A%259B%2F&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqdAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=1dc010d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E6%259F%25A5%25E9%2596%25B1%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E5%2588%2586%25E8%25AD%2589%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%258A%259B%2F&h=3804cfc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%9F%A5%E9%96%B1%E8%BA%AB%E5%88%86%E8%AD%89%E7%9A%84%E6%AC%8A%E5%8A%9B/</a><br />\n<br />\n第245章 《公安條例》第49條<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap245?xpid=ID_1438402886215_002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eleg